Package: bayesPO
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Inference for Presence-Only data
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Guido Alberti Moreira
Maintainer: Guido Moreira <guidoalber@gmail.com>
Description: Presence-Only data is best modelled with a Point Process Model.
    The work of Moreira and Gamerman (2021) provides a way to use exact Bayesian
    inference to model this type of data, which is implemented in this package.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
